name: Agricultural products subject to this chapter
text:
[§103D-104.5]  Agricultural products subject to this chapter.  The following agricultural products shall be subject to this chapter:
     (1)  Fresh meats and produce; and
     (2)  Animals and plants.
Except for the exemptions under section 103D-102(b), no exemptions under this chapter shall apply to this section. [L 2009, c 175, §3]
